You should also note (for you continued existence on the list) that the
charter specifically excludes discussion of post '83 aircooled VW buses
- a change made just after I purchased my Brazilian Camper in '98. 
As for the cost being high, here in the UK a T4 based camper would cost
50 to 60% more so you make up your own mind as to the value... 
If you have any specific questions regarding the Brazilian T2s (which
have now ceased production) please feel free to ask off list. 
Good luck
Bob Wallace
